name: Stephen Curry 2021
description: Easily one of the most influential athletes of our generation, in 2021 Steph gave us one of his best MVP caliber performances , winning the scoring title, and leading the Warriors to the Playin tournament only to end a few points shy of the Playoffs. A devastatingly premature ending for this heroic run, this is my tribute to a phenomenal effort and constant inspiration. I believe Steph when he says ....." You don't wanna see us next year"
